---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
  { name: 'Workflows', url: '/workflows' },
  { name: 'AI Copilot', url: '/workflows/ai-copilot' }
];

const faqs = [
  {
    question: 'What kind of questions can I ask the AI Copilot?',
    answer: 'Anything about your breeding program. Ask about your animals ("Which of my dogs carry the merle gene?"), your finances ("What\'s my total outstanding invoices?"), your breeding plans ("Show me all plans in the pregnancy phase"), your contacts, your waitlist, and more. The Copilot searches your actual data to answer.'
  },
  {
    question: 'Is my data safe? Does the AI share my information?',
    answer: 'Your data stays private. The AI Copilot only accesses your own breeding program data within your account. It cannot see other breeders\' data, and your conversations are not used to train AI models.'
  },
  {
    question: 'How is this different from ChatGPT or other AI tools?',
    answer: 'Generic AI tools don\'t know anything about your breeding program. They can give general advice, but they can\'t tell you which of your animals are due for vaccinations or what your revenue was last month. BreederHQ\'s AI Copilot is connected to your actual data-your animals, plans, finances, contacts, and more.'
  },
  {
    question: 'Do I need to learn special commands or syntax?',
    answer: 'No. Just type naturally, the way you\'d ask a question to an assistant. "How many litters did I have this year?" or "Show me my dogs that are ready to breed" or "What\'s the COI for my planned breeding between Luna and Max?"'
  },
  {
    question: 'Is there a limit to how many questions I can ask?',
    answer: 'Yes. Usage depends on your plan level. All plans include the Help Assistant for general breeding questions. The data-aware Copilot is available on Pro and Enterprise plans with generous daily limits.'
  },
  {
    question: 'Can the AI Copilot make changes to my data?',
    answer: 'No. The Copilot is read-only-it can search and retrieve your data to answer questions, but it cannot create, edit, or delete any records. Your data is always safe.'
  },
  {
    question: 'What if I just have a general breeding question?',
    answer: 'The Help Assistant answers general breeding and platform questions using our knowledge base of 25+ articles. It doesn\'t need access to your data-just ask things like "How do I set up a breeding plan?" or "What\'s the best way to track heat cycles?"'
  }
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="AI Copilot - Your Breeding Program Assistant | BreederHQ"
  description="Ask questions about your breeding program in plain English. BreederHQ's AI Copilot searches your animals, breeding plans, finances, and contacts to give you instant answers."
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
  faqs={faqs}
>
  <a href="#main-content" class="skip-link sr-only focus:not-sr-only focus:absolute focus:top-4 focus:left-4 focus:z-50 focus:px-4 focus:py-2 focus:bg-white focus:text-black focus:shadow-lg focus:rounded">
    Skip to content
  </a>

  <main id="main-content">
  <nav class="breadcrumb py-4 px-4 bg-gray-50" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-sm">
      <li><a href="/" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">Home</a></li>
      <li class="text-gray-400">›</li>
      <li><a href="/workflows" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">Workflows</a></li>
      <li class="text-gray-400">›</li>
      <li aria-current="page" class="text-gray-600">AI Copilot</li>
    </ol>
  </nav>

  <!-- Section 1: Hero -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Ask Your Breeding Program Anything</h1>

      <aside class="tldr-box bg-gray-100 border-l-4 border-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] p-6 my-8 rounded" role="complementary" aria-label="Page summary">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">TL;DR</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          BreederHQ includes two built-in AI assistants. The <strong>Help Assistant</strong> answers general breeding and platform questions from a knowledge base of 25+ articles. The <strong>AI Copilot</strong> goes further-it searches your actual animals, breeding plans, finances, contacts, waitlist, and offspring to answer questions about your specific program. Just type a question in plain English and get an instant, sourced answer. No special commands, no exports, no digging through spreadsheets.
        </p>
      </aside>

      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Your breeding program generates a lot of data. Animal records, breeding plans, health tests, financial transactions, buyer contacts, waitlist entries. The information is there-but finding it when you need it means clicking through screens, filtering lists, and piecing things together yourself.
      </p>

      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        What if you could just ask?
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2: The Problem -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Your Data Is Everywhere. Answers Shouldn't Be Hard to Find.</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        You know the information is in your system somewhere. But getting a specific answer still takes work:
      </p>

      <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>"How many litters did I have this year?" - open breeding plans, filter by date, count manually</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>"Which dogs carry the dilute gene?" - open each animal's genetics tab, check one by one</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>"What's my total outstanding revenue?" - open finance, look at invoices, add up the numbers</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>"Who's on my waitlist for a female?" - open waitlist, filter by preferences, cross-reference</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mr-3">•</span>
          <span>"How's my current litter doing?" - check offspring groups, weight records, care logs</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="bg-white border-l-4 border-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] p-6 rounded">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 font-semibold">
          Each question has an answer in your data. The AI Copilot finds it for you in seconds-no clicking, no filtering, no mental math.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3: AI Copilot -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">AI Copilot: Your Data, Instant Answers</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        The AI Copilot is connected to your breeding program data. Ask a question in plain English, and it searches across your animals, breeding plans, offspring, contacts, finances, and waitlist to give you a direct answer.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">🐾 Animals</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
            Search and ask about your animals by name, breed, status, genetics, or any attribute.
          </p>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1 italic">
            <p>"Show me all my intact females"</p>
            <p>"Which animals are due for vaccinations?"</p>
            <p>"Tell me about Luna's breeding history"</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">📋 Breeding Plans</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
            Check plan status, timelines, and details across your entire program.
          </p>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1 italic">
            <p>"How many litters am I expecting this spring?"</p>
            <p>"What plans are in the pregnancy phase?"</p>
            <p>"When is my next expected whelping date?"</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">💰 Finances</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
            Get instant financial summaries without opening spreadsheets.
          </p>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1 italic">
            <p>"What's my total outstanding invoices?"</p>
            <p>"How much revenue did I make this quarter?"</p>
            <p>"What are my biggest expense categories?"</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">👥 Contacts & Waitlist</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
            Find buyers, check waitlist status, and review your pipeline.
          </p>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1 italic">
            <p>"Who's waiting for a female puppy?"</p>
            <p>"How many people are on my waitlist?"</p>
            <p>"Show me contacts I haven't followed up with"</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] rounded-lg p-8 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">How It Works</h3>
        <ol class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="bg-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0 font-bold">1</span>
            <span><strong>You ask a question</strong> - in plain English, no special syntax needed</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="bg-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0 font-bold">2</span>
            <span><strong>The Copilot searches your data</strong> - it queries your animals, plans, finances, contacts, offspring, and waitlist</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="bg-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0 font-bold">3</span>
            <span><strong>You get a direct answer</strong> - with the specific information from your program, not generic advice</span>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-2">💬</div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-sm">Natural Language</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Just type like you're texting</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🔒</div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-sm">Read-Only</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Can't edit or delete your data</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-2">⚡</div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-sm">Instant Answers</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Seconds, not minutes of searching</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4: Help Assistant -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Help Assistant: Breeding Knowledge On Demand</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Not every question is about your data. Sometimes you need to know <em>how</em> to do something. The Help Assistant answers general breeding and platform questions using a built-in knowledge base of 25+ articles covering every major feature.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Platform Questions</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">•</span>
              <span>"How do I create a breeding plan?"</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">•</span>
              <span>"How do I set up my waitlist?"</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">•</span>
              <span>"How do I send an invoice?"</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">•</span>
              <span>"What is COI and why does it matter?"</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Source Citations</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
            Every answer includes links to the relevant help articles so you can read more. No guessing where the information came from.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Articles cover: animals, breeding plans, genetics, offspring, contacts, finance, waitlist, marketplace, and getting started.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border-l-4 border-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] p-6 rounded">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
          <strong>Both assistants are built into the platform.</strong> The Help Assistant is available on all plans. The AI Copilot with data access is available on Pro and Enterprise plans.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 5: Suggested Questions & Context -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Smart Suggestions Based on Where You Are</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Don't know what to ask? The AI Copilot suggests relevant questions based on which part of the platform you're using. Browsing your animals? It suggests animal-related questions. Looking at breeding plans? It suggests plan and genetics questions. On the finance page? Financial summaries.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">On the Animals Page</h3>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <div class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded border border-gray-200">"How many active animals do I have?"</div>
            <div class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded border border-gray-200">"Which females are ready to breed?"</div>
            <div class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded border border-gray-200">"Show me animals with missing health tests"</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">On the Breeding Page</h3>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <div class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded border border-gray-200">"What plans are currently active?"</div>
            <div class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded border border-gray-200">"When is my next due date?"</div>
            <div class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded border border-gray-200">"Show me plans in the weaning phase"</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">On the Finance Page</h3>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <div class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded border border-gray-200">"What's my revenue this month?"</div>
            <div class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded border border-gray-200">"How many invoices are overdue?"</div>
            <div class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded border border-gray-200">"What are my top expense categories?"</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">On the Dashboard</h3>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <div class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded border border-gray-200">"Give me an overview of my farm"</div>
            <div class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded border border-gray-200">"What needs my attention today?"</div>
            <div class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded border border-gray-200">"How's my breeding program doing?"</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        Suggestions are just a starting point. You can always type your own question about anything in your program.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 6: Interactive Tours & Help Center -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Get Up to Speed Fast</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        New to BreederHQ? The platform includes interactive guided tours and a searchable Help Center so you never feel lost.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">🎯 Interactive Tours</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
            Step-by-step walkthroughs that highlight each feature as you go. Tours launch automatically the first time you visit a new section, pointing out key buttons, explaining workflows, and getting you productive fast.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
            Dismiss tours at any time. Replay them from Settings whenever you want a refresher.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">📚 Help Center</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
            25+ searchable articles covering every major feature. Browse by module (Animals, Breeding, Offspring, Contacts, Finance, Marketplace, Genetics) or search by keyword.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
            Open the Help Center from any page without losing your place. Articles open in a slide-out panel.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border-l-4 border-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] p-6 rounded">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
          <strong>Three layers of help:</strong> Interactive tours for visual learners, the Help Center for self-service answers, and the AI assistants for everything else. You'll never need to email support for a "how do I..." question.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 7: Who This Is For -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">The AI Copilot Helps If You:</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">✓</span>
              <span>Manage a large program and need quick answers</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">✓</span>
              <span>Want financial summaries without building reports</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">✓</span>
              <span>Need to quickly find animals by genetics or status</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">✓</span>
              <span>Get asked questions by buyers and want fast answers</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">✓</span>
              <span>Prefer asking over clicking through menus</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">✓</span>
              <span>Want to learn the platform without reading documentation</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">You Might Not Need This If:</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">•</span>
              <span>You have a small program and know where everything is</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">•</span>
              <span>You prefer navigating menus and dashboards directly</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">•</span>
              <span>You don't generate enough data to need AI-powered search</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-4 italic">
            Even then, the Help Assistant is included on all plans and makes getting started much easier.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-primary text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-4">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Stop Searching. Start Asking.</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">
        Your breeding data, answered in seconds. Not minutes.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/coming-soon" class="bg-white text-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:opacity-90 inline-block">
          Get Early Access
        </a>
        <a href="/workflows/breeding-intelligence" class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-primary inline-block">
          See Breeding Intelligence →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 faq-section">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-12">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>What kind of questions can I ask the AI Copilot?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Anything about your breeding program. Ask about your animals ("Which of my dogs carry the merle gene?"), your finances ("What's my total outstanding invoices?"), your breeding plans ("Show me all plans in the pregnancy phase"), your contacts, your waitlist, and more. The Copilot searches your actual data to answer.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>Is my data safe? Does the AI share my information?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Your data stays private. The AI Copilot only accesses your own breeding program data within your account. It cannot see other breeders' data, and your conversations are not used to train AI models.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>How is this different from ChatGPT or other AI tools?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Generic AI tools don't know anything about your breeding program. They can give general advice, but they can't tell you which of your animals are due for vaccinations or what your revenue was last month. BreederHQ's AI Copilot is connected to your actual data-your animals, plans, finances, contacts, and more.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>Do I need to learn special commands or syntax?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>No. Just type naturally, the way you'd ask a question to an assistant. "How many litters did I have this year?" or "Show me my dogs that are ready to breed" or "What's the COI for my planned breeding between Luna and Max?"</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>Can the AI Copilot make changes to my data?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>No. The Copilot is read-only-it can search and retrieve your data to answer questions, but it cannot create, edit, or delete any records. Your data is always safe.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
